---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="50% Tax Break (Article 5C) Greece | Taxomade">
  <!-- Hero Section with Grid Background -->
  <div class="relative pt-40 pb-32 overflow-hidden bg-slate-50">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:24px_24px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/50 via-white/80 to-slate-50"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-8 tracking-tight">Pay tax on only half your income <br/><span class="text-blue-800">—</span> for 7 years.</h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Greece's special regime for newcomers exempts 50% of your Greek income from tax. We handle the application.</p>
      <a href="/#configurator" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold rounded-lg text-white bg-slate-900 hover:bg-blue-800 transition-colors duration-200 shadow-sm">
        See if it's worth it for you
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Two-column: What it is & Requirements -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
      <!-- What it is Card -->
      <section class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-800 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
          What it is
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          Under Greece's inbound-worker regime (Article 5C), people who move their tax residency to Greece can have <strong class="text-slate-900">50% of their Greek income exempted from income tax for up to 7 years</strong>. With standard Greek tax rates running from 9% to 44%, this can save you several thousand euros per year. It applies to both employees and freelancers/self-employed.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Requirements Card -->
      <section class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-800 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
          Requirements
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg text-slate-700 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>You must transfer your tax residency to Greece (become a Greek tax resident — i.e. stay 183+ days).</li>
          <li>You must <strong class="text-slate-900">not</strong> have been a Greek tax resident for at least <strong class="text-slate-900">5 of the previous 6 years</strong>.</li>
          <li>You must move from an EU/EEA country or a country with a tax-cooperation agreement with Greece (covers most countries: US, UK, EU, etc.).</li>
          <li>You must commit to staying in Greece for at least two years.</li>
          <li>The benefit scales with income — it's most valuable at higher incomes.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- How it works -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-20 bg-slate-50 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">How it works</h2>
      
      <div class="mb-10 bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-800 p-5 rounded-r-lg">
        <p class="text-blue-900 font-medium"><em>Timing matters:</em> The application must be filed by <strong class="text-blue-900">31 July</strong> of the relevant year. It's a one-time application that then applies for 7 years.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-6">
            <span class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold shadow-md">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">What you do</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Confirm your situation with us and provide the needed details; we tell you if and when it's worth applying.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-6">
            <span class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-800 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold shadow-md">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">What Taxomade does</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">We assess your eligibility, calculate your expected savings, prepare and file the application with the Greek tax authority (AADE), and make sure it's done within the deadline.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing Package -->
    <section class="max-w-md mx-auto mb-20">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden relative">
        <div class="p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">50% Tax Break (5C)</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6">Expert assessment and filing of your tax incentive.</p>
          <div class="flex items-baseline mb-8">
            <span class="text-5xl font-black text-slate-900">€750</span>
            <span class="text-slate-500 ml-2">/ one-off</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start text-slate-700"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-800 mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> Eligibility assessment & savings calculation</li>
            <li class="flex items-start text-slate-700"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-800 mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> Preparation of application files</li>
            <li class="flex items-start text-slate-700"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-800 mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> Submission to Greek tax authorities (AADE)</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/#contact" class="block w-full py-4 px-6 bg-slate-900 hover:bg-blue-800 text-white font-bold rounded-xl transition-colors duration-200 text-center">Start application</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-10 text-center">FAQ</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Does it work for freelancers?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Yes — employees and self-employed both qualify.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">How much can I save?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">It depends on income. At €40,000 income, roughly €5,000/year; the saving grows with income.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">How long does it last?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Up to 7 years.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">What's the catch?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">You must genuinely move your tax residency to Greece and not have been a recent Greek tax resident. We check this before applying.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Does it affect my home-country taxes?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Cross-border tax can be complex — we'll flag where you should coordinate with a home-country advisor.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
